93
00:23:03.079 --> 00:23:05.189
So they want it to be fixed.

94
00:23:05.189 --> 00:23:09.189
But we won't be able to
do that by tomorrow!

95
00:23:09.189 --> 00:23:13.289
Just leave it.
I won't go bankrupt or anything.

96
00:23:29.709 --> 00:23:31.489
