Please come back tomorrow.

103
00:23:55.879 --> 00:23:57.289
Damn it.

104
00:23:57.879 --> 00:23:59.579
Wait. young man.

105
00:23:59.579 --> 00:24:00.989
Wait just a second.

106
00:24:00.989 --> 00:24:02.789
