take for you to fix it?

116
00:24:42.579 --> 00:24:45.079
Well. about 20 to 30
minutes. at the very least.

117
00:24:46.289 --> 00:24:47.689
Aw. man.

118
00:24:47.689 --> 00:24:49.189
Thank you. ma'am.

119
00:24:50.019 --> 00:24:51.379
It was nothing.

120
00:24:51.379 --> 00:24:55.989
People like us who get paid
daily can't afford to waste a day.

121
00:24:56.539 --> 00:24:59.989
My son's in huge trouble nowadays too.
since the job market is doing so badly.

122
00:25:00.779 --> 00:25:06.489
But it's quite windy today.
Will you be all right?

123
00:25:08.579 --> 00:25:10.379
I'll be fine.

124
00:27:03.189 --> 00:27:04.379
What are you doing?

125
00:27:05.309 --> 00:27:07.989
What else?
I was just pouring wine.

126
00:27:07.989 --> 00:27:09.689
Wine. eh?

127
00:27:15.879 --> 00:27:17.489
Come on. take it slow!

128
00:27:17.489 --> 00:27:18.879
Slow down?

129
00:27:18.879 --> 00:27:20.289
That word isn't in
my vocabulary.

130
00:27:20.289 --> 00:27:21.989
I hate doing things slowly.

131
00:27:27.379 --> 00:27:28.989
Oh. just a second.

132
00:27:31.989 --> 00:27:33.989
Hello. Hello.

133
00:27:33.989 --> 00:27:36.989
- Welcome.
- Thank you.

134
